User story 
As a member of the public
So that I can buy many of my favorite bagel
I'd like to be able to add the same type of bagel to my basket more than once

Domain Model:
* Method: addquantity()
* Input:  item(which is a object)
* Source:   incase user want to add item they already have in basket, we just add the quantity or they pick item that is already in the basket without knowing  we just add the quantity 
* Output:  existingquantity + 1


